ygData.messageBody:
I would think that a SK could also help you out. Best thing to do is
auction in game (like in PoK) for it. Just make sure that you provide
the coffin.



-----Original Message-----
From: Jenn [mailto:Nefrahari@...]
Sent: Friday, September 19, 2003 11:24 AM
To: theeverquesttavern@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [The EverQuest Tavern] really need help



Okay I need some help badly from a necro on the Nameless server.

I died under the water in Everfrost, and I can't get back to my
corpse and get back out of the water. Does anyone have or know a
necro on that server who could help me get my corpse back?

Thanks

Jenn
